@startuml
title Weather Monitoring System State Transition Diagram

initial : Start

state "Initial" as Initial
state "Registered User" as RegisteredUser
state "Logged In" as LoggedIn
state "Invalid Location" as InvalidLocation
state "Valid Location" as ValidLocation
state "Weather Information" as WeatherInfo
state "View Details" as ViewDetails
state "Logged Out" as LoggedOut

Initial --> CreateAccount : User creates an account
CreateAccount --> RegisteredUser : Account creation successful

RegisteredUser --> Login : User logs in
Login --> LoggedIn : Login successful

LoggedIn --> CheckWeather : User checks weather
CheckWeather --> ValidLocation : Location is valid
ValidLocation --> SelectInfo : User selects info to check
SelectInfo --> WeatherInfo : Information selected
WeatherInfo --> ViewDetails : User views details
ViewDetails --> LoggedOut : User logs out

InvalidLocation --> InvalidLocation : No action, stay in state

LoggedOut --> Final : End of session

@enduml
